xine-lib-1.2 (1.2.4-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * vaapi isn't built (by default) on kfreebsd-*, so don't try to install it.
    (Closes: #725071)
  * Avoid a possible build failure in the vaapi plugin (delay code).

