    - Convert debian/copyright to UTF-8.
    - Add build-deps on libxv-dev and libvcdinfo-dev.
    - Bump standards version to 3.6.2
    - Make "post-Sarge"-tagged changes to debian/rules and strip debian/tmp/
      from debian/*.install.
